    "Furthermore, some depth and thermal maps featured zones with uncollectible sensor data due to frame drops, suboptimal lighting, and sensor distance disparities.",
    "To mitigate data gaps in the maps, extra attention was given to ensuring data presence around the DFU site for both modalities during image capture.",
    "It is believed that depth and thermal cameras with more similar configurations and requirements could potentially be more suitable for this purpose.Although the dataset offers valuable depth and thermal information, it has certain limitations when capturing fine-grained tissue characteristics depicted in these maps.",
    "Both cameras are specifically engineered for capturing macroscopic images, providing a broad field of view.",
    "The camera setup was intentionally designed to facilitate image capture at home for patients with restricted mobility and limited handholding capability."
